660faf5f4b6031dd35","tid":2492821,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30b342116287344ed45890dc53ca9ad73cff82a","tid":2492821,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"樓主係外國"},{"pid":"a9e4158590438cd73948e84321ea057054b6608b","tid":2492821,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"唔知蘇文隆信唔納樓主真誠叫人唔好投白票"},{"pid":"fc4cb33187872fe1dcf5b008ed59134fee6de865","tid":2492821,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"violet\"><strong>先講結論：<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">香港既意識形態越繼續關注選舉，政權既維穩就變得更容易。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n「選舉」呢樣野本身個設計就係用黎避免紛爭<br />\n而「選舉」呢樣野本身係無呢個功能<br />\n要達到呢個功能<br />\n最大既先決條件就係要<span class=\"red\"><strong>夠多人「投入／參與」</strong></span>呢場選舉，in any form<br />\n要<strong><span class=\"red\">大多數人對呢場選舉有期望</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n睇返格黎個PO<br />\n其實點解要去投白票啫？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2488295\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2488295</a><br />\n<br />\n又講到白票數目多於保皇狗得票數，又可以點點點打J點樣「階段性勝利」<br />\n又話咁樣可以變成核彈，令到外國可以開放左更多救生艇方案比香港人<br />\n又用「咁唔通咩都唔做咩」呢啲邏輯<br />\n<br />\n最抵死係又講「梁頌恆已經出聲叫人投廢票」<br />\n又玩大台<br />\n呀屌你老母唔撚記得之前solomon yue點樣玩大台？<br />\n又話之前發起開臨時政府果班係鬼<br />\n又叫香港人參選？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZP3qShvRvhaHfE7feHgrFUonvThT3XHYqj2fWE9UKkkb?filename=BoWLjup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoWLjup.jpg&h=98fa33f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">根本白票／廢票／唔投票，都唔係重點<br />\n個重點係之後啲輿論點解讀咋</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>如果蘋果呀國際新聞呀KOL國際線呀真係幫香港<br />\n每個人唔投票，呢班人自然都可以帶輿論<br />\n帶到唔投票，就係香港人既表態<br />\n咁樣又可以係「一粒核彈」啦</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">除非呢班人目的都係想香港人參與選舉幫政權維穩啫</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根本你果票廢票係架垃圾黎咋<br />\n仲係度諗到咁撚神聖可以代表到啲乜有啲咩意義係度打飛機<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">「活在幻想中」<br />\n咁撚積極參與選舉<br />\n我代政府維穩部多謝你呀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日如常生活唔得？<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">有人開PO話當日搞個黃圈感謝祭，以爆買排隊作表態，我非常支持</span></strong><br />\n19/12攪黃店感謝日, 唔得閒去投票, 無人犯法  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2487027  \" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2487027  </a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">呢場選舉以WFC既心態去面對就OK<br />\n你鐘意既去投下廢票都無乜所謂<br />\n但如果你以「又變成一粒核彈」「階段性勝利」既心態去參與<br />\n你將會繼續俾泛民撚狗咁撚</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想慣，其實仲有方法反抗！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2393573\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2393573</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPqgDeuiXeWLPq9Fm6qABdXPTWsBu6XmYCUd4y9eejdie?filename=Zt7dNH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZt7dNH4.jpg&h=becd4276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地作者哈維爾叫你係極權下要<strong><span class=\"red\">「活在真實中」<br />\n<br />\n「又變成一粒核彈」「階段性勝利」「開放救生艇」等等<br />\n全部係我眼中都係「活在幻想中」<br />\n仲對呢場選舉有期望？醒未？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0b728305a706837973034470938250efaff9a806","tid":2492821,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9e4158590438cd73948e84321ea057054b6608b","tid":2492821,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"唔知蘇文隆信唔納樓主真誠叫人唔好投白票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明眼人都知我係愛国藍絲啦"},{"pid":"d0b8f7e6ac7d40ee9c2a6d1a7747f781a4fb7ed4","tid":2492821,"uid":288824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac63db30605827fe7eaf01d4f5c9c2a490f5c68","tid":2492821,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"大家千其唔好<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">投白票</span></span></strong></span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">投白票</span></span>係唔岩架！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">投白票</span></span>係唔好架！<br />\n <br />\n叫人<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">投白票</span></span>係犯法架！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">投白票</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"我當然支持樓主, 但手指太大按錯了右邊的向下箭咀. 後見紅色的箭咀好襯色. 不過乜都好, 知道大家都知道."}]}